subject: Attention
body:
Attention
I write to inform you that your name is among the beneficiaries that
will receive their funds of US$10.5 Million (Ten Million Five Hundred
Thousand United States Dollars Only) this third quarter of the fiscal
year 2022.

subject: Re:   Attention
body:
Dear Sir/Madam,

I received your message regarding the funds of US $10.5 Million that I am supposedly set to receive this fiscal quarter. However, your message lacks specific details and a proper signature. Could you please provide more information about this matter? 

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Jessica
